									</div>
									<ul>
										<li>4 No Mod maps.</li>
										<li>3 Hidden maps.</li>
										<li>3 Hard Rock maps.</li>
										<li>3 Double Time maps.</li>
										<li>3 Tiebreaker maps.</li>
									</ul>
									<div class="page-header">
										<h4>Semifinals & Finals</h4>
									</div>
									<ul>
										<li>4 No Mod maps.</li>
										<li>4 Hidden maps.</li>
										<li>4 Hard Rock maps.</li>
										<li>4 Double Time maps.</li>
										<li>3 Tiebreaker maps.</li>
									</ul>
									<div class="page-header">
										<h4>Grand Finals</h4>
									</div>
									<ul>
										<li>5 No Mod maps.</li>
										<li>4 Hidden maps.</li>
										<li>4 Hard Rock maps.</li>
										<li>4 Double Time maps.</li>
										<li>3 Tiebreaker maps.</li>
									</ul>
									<br>
									<p>In a freemod pick, each team is required to have at least one player to play with at least 1 mod, restricted to
										Hidden, Hard Rock and/or Easy and permitted to pick a combination of these mods.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
		</div>
